    "rationale": "All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors assessed. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed required gradation levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions at Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is offset by the strength of the multi-laboratory experimental dataset, the tight E/uval metrics across all QoIs, and the conservative acceptance bounds applied. Overall model credibility is sufficient to support the Medium-risk COU decision for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw 510(k) submission.",
